l you are able to run at ungodly speeds.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#303030"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">OzFactor</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial"><A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/ozfactorcpk" TARGET=_blank>Follow the on-screen instructions to download a strafe-jumping tutorial.</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#303030"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">OzFactor</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Oh, and don't try to download the LTJ song, it doesn't work.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
